						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment of 20 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold deposited with the Tiruvōṇagaṇapperumakkaḷ at Tiruchcheṅgōḍu by one Araṭṭaṉ Nakkaṉ's son on behalf of <hi rend="bold">Maṇikaṇṭi-Ōḍaiyamandāḷ a lady residing at Irōḍu</hi> (Erode), for feeding 20 Brāhmaṇas (once) every month (probably on the Tiruvōṇam day).</p>						

						</summary>
